RawLine: SDM_1104707552,【原來如此…此心法口訣中七星對應人體七竅，透過內力在七竅穴位中流轉，達到去穢補體之效。】,【原来如此…此心法口诀中七星对应人体七窍，透过内力在七窍穴位中流转，达到去秽补体之效。】

Items.mt: <[>I see... The seven stars in this technique correspond to the seven orifices of the human body, and through the flow of internal energy in the seven orifices, the effect of removing filth and replenishing the body is achieved. <]>
